{"about_the_game":"Savage Gears is a violent, single-player FPS inspired by early 2000s objective-oriented action games. <br>Armed with an Iron Fist and an arsenal of devastating weaponry, you play as Ero Lei'Bourne, a fearless soldier, on his dangerous mission to save the continent from the brink of annihilation.<br><br><strong>STORY</strong><br>Set in alternate history East Africa, you follow the journey of Ero Lei'Bourne on a Special Forces operation to thwart an arms race conspiracy ... or die trying. <br><br><strong>FEATURES</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Experience intense action in the single-player campaign<br></li><li> Wield a range of fictional sci-fi-inspired weapons<br></li><li> Harness the power of the Iron Fist as you Smash your way through enemies in intense, first-person combat<br></li><li> Fight against a dynamic range of relentless hordes of mercenaries, drones, and experimental mutant soldiers<br></li><li> Explore a diverse range of environments from Fort Speke to train levels to forest environments and more </li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053340/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1731430491","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053340/page.bg.jpg?t=1731430491","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053340/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1731430491","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053340/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1731430491","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[2,5],"notes":"May contain violence & gore"},"demos":[{"appid":3219860,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"Savage Gears is a violent, single-player FPS inspired by early 2000s objective-oriented action games. <br>Armed with an Iron Fist and an arsenal of devastating weaponry, you play as Ero Lei'Bourne,